# Security Policy

## Supported Versions

| Version | Supported          |
| ------- | ------------------ |
| 2.3.9   | :white_check_mark: |
| 2.3.8   | :white_check_mark: |
| 2.3.7   | :x:                |
| < 2.3.7 | :x:                |

## Reporting a Vulnerability

To report a Vulnerability open a issue on Github or send a mail to info@domipas.nl
